This is the new LibreCAD Kernel. With keeping in mind the extensibilty, modularity and the design, the LibreCAD is divided into 3 parts.
1) The UI
2) The kernel
3) The CADViewer


Compilation Instructions

Install boost
Install Qt >4.8 or better Qt 5
Install git

git clone --recursive https://github.com/rvt/kerneldev 

qmake -r
make -j 4



Ubuntu/Mint
========

apt-get install qttools5-dev qttools5-dev-tools libqt5opengl5-dev liblua5.2-dev git g++ gcc-4.8